9fab65b2-692a-459e-880b-04d20609d99c.title: Tool Leprechaun
9fab65b2-692a-459e-880b-04d20609d99c.text:
Ah, 'tis a foine day to be sure! Were yez wantin' me to
store yer tools, or maybe ye might be wantin' yer stuff
back from me?

options.text: What do you do with the tools you're storing?
No thanks, I'll keep hold of my stuff.

1b2b48e7-304e-45a3-aa18-0cec2a5491c1.title: Tool Leprechaun
1b2b48e7-304e-45a3-aa18-0cec2a5491c1.text:
We'll hold onto yer rake, yer seed dibber, yer spade,
yer secateurs, yer waterin' can and yer trowel - but
mind it's not one of them fancy trowels only
archaeologists use!

a793fdd0-ae95-4e67-b8df-8cac27f26b96.title: Tool Leprechaun
a793fdd0-ae95-4e67-b8df-8cac27f26b96.text:
We'll take a few buckets off yer hands too, and even
yer compost, supercompost an' ultracompost! Also plant
cure vials.

25f9cb0a-c458-4ae9-b389-930005acf1c8.title: Tool Leprechaun
25f9cb0a-c458-4ae9-b389-930005acf1c8.text:
Aside from that, if ye hands me yer farming produce, I
can mebbe change it into banknotes for ye.

7892b633-adec-415c-a651-ecebb8962a21.title: Tool Leprechaun
7892b633-adec-415c-a651-ecebb8962a21.text: So... do ye want to be using the store?

options.text: What do you do with the tools you're storing?
No thanks, I'll keep hold of my stuff.

d33f7f72-48bf-4119-a9c8-eb2dc1dc46a3.title: <player>
d33f7f72-48bf-4119-a9c8-eb2dc1dc46a3.text:
What do you do with the tools you're storing?
They can't possibly all fit in your pockets!

e916dfee-b78f-41bf-ab4f-bc52f5801cbf.title: Tool Leprechaun
e916dfee-b78f-41bf-ab4f-bc52f5801cbf.text:
We leprechauns have a shed where we keep 'em. It's a
magic shed, so ye can get yer items back from any of
us leprechauns whenever ye want. Saves ye havin' to
carry loads of stuff around the country!

options.text: No thanks, I'll keep hold of my stuff.

b4c233bf-494d-4c2f-b2bb-1ae2e8491351.title: <player>
b4c233bf-494d-4c2f-b2bb-1ae2e8491351.text: No thanks, I'll keep hold of my stuff.

6bcea3fb-3e73-4d51-84f3-ffcf909ba5fb.title: Tool Leprechaun
6bcea3fb-3e73-4d51-84f3-ffcf909ba5fb.text:
Ye must be dafter than ye look if ye likes luggin' yer
tools everywhere ye goes!
